Third-party model weights bundled in the ONNX artifacts
=======================================================

These ONNX files are derivative weights. Attribution and full license texts
for each upstream source are provided in this directory.

1. Irodori-TTS-500M-v3  (dit / text_encoder / speaker_encoder / duration)
   https://huggingface.co/Aratako/Irodori-TTS-500M-v3
   License: MIT — see Irodori-TTS-LICENSE

2. Semantic-DACVAE-Japanese-32dim  (dacvae_encoder / dacvae_decoder)
   https://huggingface.co/Aratako/Semantic-DACVAE-Japanese-32dim
   License: MIT — see Semantic-DACVAE-LICENSE
   Derived from facebook/dacvae-watermarked
   (https://huggingface.co/facebook/dacvae-watermarked).

3. llm-jp-3-150m tokenizer  (tokenizer/llmjp_tok/)
   https://huggingface.co/llm-jp/llm-jp-3-150m
   License: Apache-2.0 — see llm-jp-3-150m-LICENSE

Modifications made to the upstream weights (per Apache-2.0 §4(b)):
  - PyTorch -> ONNX export (dynamo, symbolic shapes)
  - Complex RoPE replaced with a real-valued equivalent for ONNX export
  - Data-dependent guards in the duration predictor bypassed at export
  - fp16 conversion of all components
  - Decoder ConvTranspose layers rewritten to a Conv-only sub-pixel form
